[thinking] Now, I'm also wondering about dynamic class names, specifically in the ProgrammaticClientEndpoint inner class. It includes a `$`, which could be okay depending on file naming rules. However, the overloaded connectToServer methods might present a potential issue with URI schemes and null configurators that could arise before getting to the metadata phase. This needs further reasoning!
